title: Staying Positive in the Negative Sense
itunes:title: Staying Positive in the Negative Sense
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha got COVID too. She shares her experience quarantining at home and swaps watch recommendations with Kate to help pass the time. Although Leisha doesn’t seem to appreciate classic cinema the way Kate does…Kate’s words, not ours.
